</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-26_ pf-text-1">Research suggests that individuals with autism and learning disabilities often face stigma, discrimination, and barriers to accessing education, employment, and healthcare services, underscoring the urgent need for awareness and support.





































